# Mailbox Agent Notes

This is an afmail mailbox workspace. Write mailbox-specific agent behavior,
priorities, reply style, escalation rules, and user preferences here. Keep
custom instructions outside the afmail managed block below.

<!-- BEGIN afmail managed -->
## afmail Workspace Rules

For afmail operations, follow the installed `agent-first-mail` skill. If the
skill is missing, run `afmail skill install` and restart the agent so it reloads
skills.

Do not manually edit `.afmail/` except `.afmail/templates/`; other files are
machine-managed state. Use `afmail` for message disposition, case membership,
archive changes, push queue changes, and remote effects.

Match agent-authored reasons, case/archive names, summaries, notes, and draft
bodies to `.afmail/config.json` `workspace.language_bcp47` unless the user asks
for another language. Put mailbox-specific exceptions in this user-editable file.
<!-- END afmail managed -->
